laboratory_examinations.findings: Moderate to severe patent steatosis with a fat fraction of 22%; The pancreas is atrophic with low T1 signal progressive enhancement; Mild irregularity of a non-dilated pancreatic duct with multiple ectatic side branches; Low signal intensity stranding adjacent to pancreatic tail has significantly improved compared to prior CT.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Significantly improved low signal intensity stranding adjacent to pancreatic tail compared to prior imaging.
